OL,7,FA serial rapist who drugged victims
OL,8,Fand hid multiple cameras in his home
OL,9,Fhas pleaded guilty to a string of
OL,10,Fsexual offences against at least 12
OL,11,Fwomen, as detectives appealed for more
OL,12,Fvictims to come forward.
OL,14,FChao Xu, 33, of Greenwich, south-east
OL,15,FLondon, pleaded guilty to 24 sexual
OL,16,Foffences that were carried out over
OL,17,Fthe course of three years at a plea
OL,18,Fand trial preparation hearing at
OL,19,FWoolwich Crown Court on Friday.
