OL,7,FThe defendant is from China and is
OL,8,Fbelieved to have lived in the UK since
OL,9,F2013.
OL,11,FHe admitted four counts of rape, eight
OL,12,Fcounts of assault by penetration, four
OL,13,Fcounts of sexual assault, four counts
OL,14,Fof voyeurism, two counts of
OL,15,Fadministering a substance with intent,
OL,16,Fand two counts of operating equipment
OL,17,Fbeneath the clothing of another
OL,18,Fwithout consent between February 2022
OL,19,Fand June 2025.
